column6: SELECT count() FROM zeros(2000000) WHERE NOT ignore(visitParamExtractRaw(materialize(\'{"myparam":{"nested_1":"test_string","nested_2":"test_2"}}\'), \'myparam\'))
INSERT INTO codec_mon_UInt64_NONE (n) SELECT number*512+(intHash64(number)%512) FROM system.numbers LIMIT 10000000 SETTINGS max_threads=1
